    "en": {
      "title": "The fuel truck also stops on the way without fuel",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A bowser carrying petrol from the Muthurajawela fuel refinery to the Puttalam fuel station was stopped on the way for nearly 10 hours when it ran out of fuel.",
        "It is said that the one that stopped on the highway without fuel was a bouser owned by a private distributor carrying 19,800 liters of petrol that was brought to three Puttalam fuel stations.",
        "When the bowser ran out of fuel, its driver informed a few nearby fuel stations, but they said that diesel was not provided from the fuel stations."
      ],
